getPassword

public java.lang.String getPassword()
Description copied from interface: FileAreaAdmin
Returns the password of the operating system user that owns files transferred into this File Area. Note that the password is obfuscated if a password is actually set. If Null is returned this indicates that no password is set, which may be the case when the user is specified as a credential set.

Specified by:
